        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Ignoring the Income Threshold</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">€2,300 is firm. If you're just under, authorities won't round up. Build savings proof or increase income before applying.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
